---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro'
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
import { SEO } from "astro-seo";
import '../styles/common.css';

const seo = {
  title: 'Cloudopt | Cloud Solutions & Expertise | Who we are',
  site_name: 'cloudopt',
  description: 'Based in Melbourne, Cloudopt specializes in tailored cloud technology solutions centred around architecture, engineering, modernisation, and transformation.',
  type: 'website',
}
---

<!-- Start of the layout component -->
<Layout seo={seo}>
  <!-- Start of the container component -->
  <Container narrow>
    <!-- Navigation links -->
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">home</a>
      <a href="/services">services</a>
      <a href="/whoweare">who we are</a>
      <a href="mailto:contact@cloudopt.com.au?subject=hello" target="_blank">contact</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Hero article -->
    <article class="hero__article">
      <h2 class="fade-in">who we are</h2>
    <!-- Body of text -->
    <section>
      <p class="fade-in p-whoweare">
        <br>
        Based out of Melbourne, Cloudopt specialises in architecture, engineering, automation, and the transformation and modernisation of technology infrastructures comprising a diverse range of technologies across public, private and hybrid clouds.
        <br><br>
        We don't just facilitate companies in their journey to the cloud, we also optimise existing cloud and technology systems. By identifying gaps and opportunities across your technology portfolio, we focus on automation, enhancement, simplification, and cost efficiency.
        <br><br>
        At Cloudopt, we're not just about implementing technology; we're about transforming your business and capabilities. Not only are we focused on the technology, but also how enhancing governance, process, upskilling and ways of working can uplift existing internal capability and add immense value to your business.
        <br><br>
        Our experience spans diverse sectors in Australia and the UK, including finance, health, logistics, transport, defence, air traffic control and energy. Cloudopt are uniquely positioned to understand industry-specific challenges, enabling us to deliver best practice solutions tailored to you.
        <br><br>
        Choosing Cloudopt means embracing the present and preparing for the future. As your partner in cloud technology, we are committed to maximising cloud technology's potential, ensuring your business doesn't settle for just keeping pace, but leads in your industry.
      </p>
    </section>
    </article>
  </Container>
</Layout>
